{"tid":1448651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(救救中共) 懇請各位香港人防止支爆","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:41:52.000Z","uid":270858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d5315d6b5a7f4525236ca4216a2f22a88bed8bac","tid":1448651,"uid":270858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"我地要[b<span style=\"color: red;\">]挽留</span>[/b]其香港進入大陸的外資 不可讓其撤資 &lt;- <strong>保護</strong>中國銀行及各主要融資機構<br />\n&quot;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">防止</span></strong>&quot; 制造金融危機 加速中國支爆<br />\n在各關口<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停止輸出</span></strong> 香港賴以成功的價值觀(法治,透明,人權,自由)予內地同胞 以及 中共的統治術 謊言,仇恨,暴力,意識形態的嘮叨重覆!  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不可以</span></strong>動搖同胞的思想堅定<br />\n向無產階級<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">禁絕提及</span></strong> 中共失信 及 權貴資本主義, 樓奴政治.<br />\n建立以blockchain-based 的 香港人行管理 web page, 確保每個人都能自行補位,新增職位!"},{"pid":"8b38dfeff7812430bbfdd2bf4b31e26556845b86","tid":1448651,"uid":79039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"TVB：銅鑼灣有穿黑衣男子協助警方拘捕示威者 警方暫未回覆<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448265</a>"},{"pid":"869295212824f89df3d2f23308c8dd84aa862692","tid":1448651,"uid":270858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:59.000Z","msg":"推一推 保護中共"},{"pid":"a1e3cc615efee76147e8716189c8c92920a6496c","tid":1448651,"uid":270858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:00:51.000Z","msg":"推一推 保護中共"},{"pid":"5c829707c6a466e5cbe76ccf17c26d281ed5b16c","tid":1448651,"uid":270858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"推一推 救救中共"}]}